pageTitle: North Devon Wheelers Southfork Youth Series #5Events - British Cycling
textBeforeTable: The Races North Devon Wheelers Southfork Tour of Tesco Youth Series Race 5 of 6 The race is held on a technical circuit with a mixture of sweeping and tight bends allowing riders to demonstrate their cornering and sprinting skills resulting in fast and exciting races. Toilet facilities present. Signing on for all riders commences 30 minutes before the race start time. Riders brief for all categories held 10 minutes before the race start time. Category E riders to commence racing on their own. Once the Category E riders have finished Category C and D riders to race, on completion Category A and B riders to race.
